      • NurInventoryExtended

        public NurInventoryExtended()
        Basic inventory parameter constructor: Q, session and rounds are not initialized. Transit time, target and selection state are set to 0, "all" and "all" respectively. See { @link #com.nordicid.nurapi.INVTARGET_A } and { @link #com.nordicid.nurapi.INVSELSTATE_ALL }.

      • NurInventoryExtended

        public NurInventoryExtended(int Q,
                            int session,
                            int rounds)
        Extended inventory parameters with Q, session and rounds defined.
        Parameters:
        Q - Q to be used during a single inventory round.
        session - Session to be used throughout the inventories.s
        rounds - Maximum number of module's internal inventory rounds.
        See Also:
        transitTime, inventoryTarget, inventorySelState
